## Current Safety / Validation Rules

- Food listings must use approved active menu items from that mess.
- Waste logs must use a valid active menu item from that mess.
- Student feedback is always associated with a mess.

## Removed Module

### Cook Reviews
- Cook Reviews has been removed from:
  - frontend routes
  - dashboard navigation
  - backend route mounting
  - database model usage
- Any future recreation of the app should treat Cook Reviews as removed unless intentionally reintroduced.
